title: Couple With Heart Woman No Skin Tone Man Dark Skin Tone
alsoKnownAs: Man and Woman Holding Hands With Heart
description: A couple embracing, with a heart between them, symbolizing romantic love and partnership. This specific combination features a woman with no specified skin tone and a man with a dark skin tone.
apple_vendor_description: This couple with heart emoji on Apple devices depicts a tender embrace between a woman and a man, with the woman rendered in a neutral, light skin tone and the man in a rich, dark skin tone, reflecting Apple’s dedication to diverse representation. A bright, glowing heart floats between them, rendered with Apple's signature glossy 3D shading and soft rounded edges, symbolizing deep affection and love. The realistic lighting and smooth gradients on the figures convey warmth and connection, making this emoji a beautiful way to express romantic love, partnership, and family bonds in digital communication.
